{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895845795,"sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba40891001e8AFJP3KK3Kmok","messageID":"msg_d7ba3e8e6001xkvtcTrke1k47G","sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-0440eb036c534800a4f9a9bcae71c798","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) |\n8: | Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: [TO BE FILLED: Define scope for Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)]\n16: \n17: ## Out of Scope\n18: \n19: [TO BE FILLED: Define out of scope items]\n20: \n21: ## Dependencies\n22: \n23: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n24: |------------|---------|---------|\n25: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n26: \n27: ## Deliverables\n28: \n29: | File | Description |\n30: |------|-------------|\n31: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n32: \n33: ## Acceptance Criteria\n34: \n35: - [ ] [TO BE FILLED]\n36: \n37: ## References\n38: \n39: - [TO BE FILLED: Add relevant references]\n\n(End of file - total 39 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) |\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define scope for Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)]\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define out of scope items]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/spec.md","time":{"start":1775895845742,"end":1775895845794}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895845797,"sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba40c80001WWJL4iTrUKfLYg","messageID":"msg_d7ba3e8e6001xkvtcTrke1k47G","sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-2c5e28e338b4496694789578347cc2c5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-038 |\n8: | Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立完善的单元测试体系，确保代码质量和稳定性。该模块是 AgentCube 的核心 HTTP 服务框架，负责 Sandbox 生命周期管理、路由、中间件、健康检查和错误处理。现有的测试覆盖了主要功能路径，但需要增强边界条件测试、并发安全测试、性能基准测试和更复杂的集成测试场景。\n17: \n18: ---\n19: \n20: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n21: \n22: ### 2.1 In Scope\n23: \n24: | Deliverable | Description |\n25: |-------------|-------------|\n26: | 增强现有测试覆盖 | 为现有测试文件添加边界条件、错误路径和并发安全测试 |\n27: | 表驱动测试重构 | 将简单测试重构为表驱动测试，提高可维护性和覆盖率 |\n28: | Benchmark 测试 | 为关键组件添加性能基准测试 (MemoryStore, GarbageCollector, LifecycleManager) |\n29: | Mock/Fake 增强 | 完善 mockLogger、mockHealthChecker 等测试辅助类型 |\n30: | 新增测试场景 | 添加以下测试场景：Context 取消、超时处理、并发竞争、资源泄漏检测 |\n31: | 测试覆盖率报告 | 配置 `go test -cover` 并设定目标覆盖率 ≥ 80% |\n32: | CI 集成 | 确保 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 在 CI 中自动执行 |\n33: \n34: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n35: \n36: | Item | Reason |\n37: |------|--------|\n38: | e2e 测试 | 已有 integration_test.go 覆盖基本 E2E 场景，大型 E2E 测试应单独 AR |\n39: | 修改业务代码 | 本 AR 仅关注测试增强，不修改生产代码逻辑 |\n40: | Kubernetes 集群真实测试 | 使用 fake client 即可，真实集群测试属于集成测试范畴 |\n41: | 代码覆盖率 100% | 不切实际，重点覆盖核心逻辑和边界条件 |\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n46: \n47: ### 3.1 新增文件\n48: \n49: | File | Description |\n50: |------|-------------|\n51: | `pkg/workloadmanager/benchmark_test.go` | 性能基准测试 |\n52: | `pkg/workloadmanager/fakes/fake_store.go` | 可配置的 Fake Store 实现 |\n53: | `pkg/workloadmanager/fakes/fake_k8s_client.go` | Fake K8sClient 实现 |\n54: | `pkg/workloadmanager/mocks/mock_store.go` | Mock Store (使用 testify/mock) |\n55: \n56: ### 3.2 修改文件\n57: \n58: | File | Change |\n59: |------|--------|\n60: | `store_test.go` | 添加表驱动测试、并发压力测试、边界条件测试 |\n61: | `lifecycle_test.go` | 添加 Context 取消/超时测试、SandboxClaim 删除错误路径测试 |\n62: | `garbage_collector_test.go` | 添加 GC 频率测试、Stop 后再 Start 测试、内存泄漏检测 |\n63: | `server_test.go` | 添加 GracefulShutdown 测试、多 Handler 注册测试 |\n64: | `k8s_client_test.go` | 添加 ClientCache 并发访问测试、错误路径测试 |\n65: | `types_test.go` | 添加 ConflictError 测试、JSON 序列化/反序列化边界测试 |\n66: | `informers_test.go` | 添加多 Informer 测试、启动顺序测试 |\n67: | `handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go` | 添加 Force 删除测试、GracePeriodSeconds 测试、错误响应格式测试 |\n68: \n69: ### 3.3 Upstream Dependencies\n70: \n71: | Dependency | Purpose |\n72: |------------|---------|\n73: | `github.com/stretchr/testify` | 断言和 Mock 框架 |\n74: | `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake` | Kubernetes fake client |\n75: | `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` | Dynamic client fake |\n76: | `github.com/go-chi/chi/v5` | 路由框架测试 |\n77: \n78: ### 3.4 Downstream Consumers\n79: \n80: | Consumer | Usage |\n81: |----------|-------|\n82: | CI Pipeline | 自动执行 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` |\n83: | 开发者 | PR 提交前运行本地测试 |\n84: | Release 流程 | 确保测试通过后才发布 |\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n89: \n90: ### 方案 A: 保持现状，仅维护现有测试\n91: \n92: **优点**: 无需额外工作量\n93: **缺点**: 测试覆盖率不足，潜在问题难以发现\n94: **结论**: 拒绝，风险过高\n95: \n96: ### 方案 B: 使用 Ginkgo/BDD 测试框架\n97: \n98: **优点**: 更好的测试组织、可读性高\n99: **缺点**: 需要引入新框架、团队需要学习、与现有 testify 不一致\n100: **结论**: 拒绝，保持现有 testify 一致性\n101: \n102: ### 方案 C: 使用 testify/mock 替代手写 mock\n103: \n104: **优点**: 标准化 Mock、更灵活的期望配置\n105: **缺点**: 需要重构现有手写 mock、增加复杂度\n106: **结论**: 部分接受，仅在新增复杂 Mock 时使用\n107: \n108: ### 方案 D: 使用 go-cmp 进行深度比较\n109: \n110: **优点**: 更精确的结构比较、忽略零值\n111: **缺点**: 引入新依赖、与 testify/assert 功能重叠\n112: **结论**: 拒绝，现有 assert.DeepEqual 足够\n113: \n114: ---\n115: \n116: ## 5. Risks\n117: \n118: | Risk | Mitigation |\n119: |------|------------|\n120: | 测试代码与生产代码耦合过紧 | 使用 Interface 和 Mock/Fake 保持隔离 |\n121: | 并发测试引入假阳性 | 使用 `-race` 检测、避免共享状态 |\n122: | Fake client 行为与真实 cluster 不一致 | 明确 Fake 的局限性，关键路径需集成测试验证 |\n123: | 测试执行时间过长影响 CI | Benchmark 测试分离、使用 `-short` 跳过慢测试 |\n124: | 测试维护成本高 | 表驱动测试减少重复代码、测试辅助函数封装 |\n125: \n126: ---\n127: \n128: ## 6. Implementation Checklist\n129: \n130: - [ ] 创建 benchmark_test.go，包含 MemoryStore/GarbageCollector/LifecycleManager 基准测试\n131: - [ ] 创建 fakes/fake_store.go 和 fakes/fake_k8s_client.go\n132: - [ ] 重构 store_test.go 为表驱动测试\n133: - [ ] 添加 lifecycle_test.go Context 取消/超时测试\n134: - [ ] 添加 garbage_collector_test.go Stop/Start 循环测试\n135: - [ ] 添加 k8s_client_test.go ClientCache 并发测试\n136: - [ ] 添加 server_test.go GracefulShutdown 信号处理测试\n137: - [ ] 添加 handlers/sandbox_delete_test.go Force 删除和 GracePeriod 测试\n138: - [ ] 配置 CI 测试覆盖率报告 (目标 ≥ 80%)\n139: - [ ] 添加 Makefile 目标 `make test-workloadmanager`\n140: - [ ] 文档化测试辅助类型使用方法\n141: \n142: ---\n143: \n144: ## 7. References\n145: \n146: - [client-go library spec](../../../deployment/client-go.md) — Kubernetes client 生成规范\n147: - [Kubernetes fake client documentation](https://pkg.go.dev/k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake)\n148: - [testify documentation](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/stretchr/testify)\n149: - [Go testing best practices](https://go.dev/blog/table-driven-tests)\n\n(End of file - total 149 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-038 |\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立完善的单元测试体系，确保代码质量和稳定性。该模块是 AgentCube 的核心 HTTP 服务框架，负责 Sandbox 生命周期管理、路由、中间件、健康检查和错误处理。现有的测试覆盖了主要功能路径，但需要增强边界条件测试、并发安全测试、性能基准测试和更复杂的集成测试场景。\n\n---\n\n## 2. Scope (范围)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775895845745,"end":1775895845796}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895845799,"sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba41b1b001kjt0Jb7jKE1XvX","messageID":"msg_d7ba3e8e6001xkvtcTrke1k47G","sessionID":"ses_2845c51e5ffeHW8ywQ2rHowlPW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3c0465834bab498fa1bdc174fcca13c4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package workloadmanager\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"time\"\n6: \n7: \tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n8: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n9: \t\"k8s.io/utils/ptr\"\n10: \n11: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n12: )\n13: \n14: type LifecycleConfig struct {\n15: \tDefaultTTL          time.Duration\n16: \tDefaultIdleTimeout  time.Duration\n17: \tDefaultMaxDuration  time.Duration\n18: \tGCInterval          time.Duration\n19: \tGCOnceTimeout       time.Duration\n20: \tDeletionGracePeriod int64\n21: \tDeletionTimeout     time.Duration\n22: }\n23: \n24: func DefaultLifecycleConfig() LifecycleConfig {\n25: \treturn LifecycleConfig{\n26: \t\tDefaultTTL:          DefaultSandboxTTL,\n27: \t\tDefaultIdleTimeout:  DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout,\n28: \t\tDefaultMaxDuration:  DefaultMaxSessionDuration,\n29: \t\tGCInterval:          GarbageCollectorInterval,\n30: \t\tGCOnceTimeout:       2 * time.Minute,\n31: \t\tDeletionGracePeriod: 0,\n32: \t\tDeletionTimeout:     SandboxDeleteTimeout,\n33: \t}\n34: }\n35: \n36: type SandboxLifecycleManager struct {\n37: \tk8sClient *K8sClient\n38: \tstore     Store\n39: \tconfig    LifecycleConfig\n40: \tlogger    Logger\n41: }\n42: \n43: func NewSandboxLifecycleManager(k8sClient *K8sClient, store Store, config LifecycleConfig, logger Logger) *SandboxLifecycleManager {\n44: \treturn &SandboxLifecycleManager{\n45: \t\tk8sClient: k8sClient,\n46: \t\tstore:     store,\n47: \t\tconfig:    config,\n48: \t\tlogger:    logger,\n49: \t}\n50: }\n51: \n52: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) DeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error {\n53: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, m.config.DeletionTimeout)\n54: \tdefer cancel()\n55: \n56: \tsandboxInfo, err := m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n57: \tif err != nil {\n58: \t\tif _, ok := err.(*NotFoundError); ok {\n59: \t\t\treturn &NotFoundError{Resource: \"session\", Name: sessionID}\n60: \t\t}\n61: \t\treturn &InternalError{Err: err}\n62: \t}\n63: \n64: \tdeleteOpts := metav1.DeleteOptions{\n65: \t\tGracePeriodSeconds: ptr.To(m.config.DeletionGracePeriod),\n66: \t}\n67: \n68: \terr = m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(SandboxGVR).\n69: \t\tNamespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n70: \t\tDelete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n71: \n72: \tif err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n73: \t\treturn handleDeleteError(err)\n74: \t}\n75: \n76: \tif sandboxInfo.Kind == types.SandboxClaimKind {\n77: \t\terr = m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(SandboxClaimGVR).\n78: \t\t\tNamespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n79: \t\t\tDelete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n80: \n81: \t\tif err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n82: \t\t\tm.logger.Error(\"failed to delete SandboxClaim\", \"sandboxName\", sandboxInfo.SandboxName, \"err\", err)\n83: \t\t}\n84: \t}\n85: \n86: \terr = m.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n87: \tif err != nil {\n88: \t\tm.logger.Error(\"failed to delete from store\", \"sessionID\", sessionID, \"err\", err)\n89: \t}\n90: \n91: \treturn nil\n92: }\n93: \n94: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) IsExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo) bool {\n95: \treturn time.Now().After(sandbox.ExpiresAt)\n96: }\n97: \n98: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) IsIdleExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo, idleTimeout time.Duration) bool {\n99: \tif sandbox.LastActivity.IsZero() {\n100: \t\treturn false\n101: \t}\n102: \treturn time.Now().After(sandbox.LastActivity.Add(idleTimeout))\n103: }\n104: \n105: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) ForceDeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error {\n106: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, m.config.DeletionTimeout)\n107: \tdefer cancel()\n108: \n109: \tsandboxInfo, err := m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n110: \tif err != nil {\n111: \t\tif _, ok := err.(*NotFoundError); ok {\n112: \t\t\treturn nil\n113: \t\t}\n114: \t\treturn &InternalError{Err: err}\n115: \t}\n116: \n117: \tdeleteOpts := metav1.DeleteOptions{\n118: \t\tGracePeriodSeconds: ptr.To[int64](0),\n119: \t}\n120: \n121: \terr = m.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(SandboxGVR).\n122: \t\tNamespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n123: \t\tDelete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n124: \n125: \tif err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n126: \t\tm.logger.Error(\"force delete sandbox CR failed\", \"sandboxName\", sandboxInfo.SandboxName, \"err\", err)\n127: \t}\n128: \n129: \tif sandboxInfo.Kind == types.SandboxClaimKind {\n130: \t\tm.k8sClient.DynamicClient().Resource(SandboxClaimGVR).\n131: \t\t\tNamespace(sandboxInfo.SandboxNamespace).\n132: \t\t\tDelete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, deleteOpts)\n133: \t}\n134: \n135: \terr = m.store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n136: \tif err != nil {\n137: \t\tm.logger.Error(\"failed to delete from store during force delete\", \"sessionID\", sessionID, \"err\", err)\n138: \t}\n139: \n140: \treturn nil\n141: }\n142: \n143: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error) {\n144: \treturn m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n145: }\n146: \n147: func (m *SandboxLifecycleManager) UpdateSandboxStatus(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, status string) error {\n148: \tsandbox, err := m.store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)\n149: \tif err != nil {\n150: \t\treturn err\n151: \t}\n152: \n153: \tsandbox.Status = status\n154: \treturn m.store.UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox)\n155: }\n156: \n157: func handleDeleteError(err error) error {\n158: \tif apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n159: \t\treturn nil\n160: \t}\n161: \tif apierrors.IsConflict(err) {\n162: \t\treturn &ConflictError{Resource: \"sandbox\", Err: err}\n163: \t}\n164: \treturn &InternalError{Err: err}\n165: }\n166: \n167: func determineDeletionReason(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo, now time.Time, idleTimeout time.Duration) DeletionReason {\n168: \tif now.After(sandbox.ExpiresAt) {\n169: \t\treturn DeletionReasonMaxDurationReached\n170: \t}\n171: \tif !sandbox.LastActivity.IsZero() && now.After(sandbox.LastActivity.Add(idleTimeout)) {\n172: \t\treturn DeletionReasonIdleTimeout\n173: \t}\n174: \treturn DeletionReasonUserRequest\n175: }\n\n(End of file - total 175 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package workloadmanager\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n\t\"k8s.io/utils/ptr\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n)\n\ntype LifecycleConfig struct {\n\tDefaultTTL          time.Duration\n\tDefaultIdleTimeout  time.Duration\n\tDefaultMaxDuration  time.Duration\n\tGCInterval          time.Duration\n\tGCOnceTimeout       time.Duration\n\tDeletionGracePeriod int64","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go","time":{"start":1775895845754,"end":1775895845798}}}}
